# ============================================================================
#  Expense Machine — environment configuration (all optional)
# ============================================================================
#
# The app runs fully offline with NONE of these set. Each variable activates an
# optional cloud capability at build time (Vite inlines VITE_* vars).
#
# Copy to `.env.local` and fill in to enable.

# --- Cloud persistence (Phase 13) ------------------------------------------
# Create a project at https://supabase.com, run src/features/backend/db/schema.sql,
# then paste your project URL and public anon key here. Row Level Security in the
# schema keeps the anon key safe for the browser.
# VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://YOUR-PROJECT.supabase.co
# VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=YOUR-PUBLIC-ANON-KEY

# --- AI provider seam (Phase 15) -------------------------------------------
# ⚠️  SECURITY: DO NOT set these in a client-side build. VITE_* vars are
# inlined into the JavaScript bundle and visible to anyone inspecting the page.
# The remote provider is disabled at runtime to prevent credential leaks.
# A real LLM integration MUST proxy through a backend service.
# VITE_ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=
# VITE_OPENAI_API_KEY=
